@startuml aeb_pressure_to_ehb_command_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title AEB Pressure To EHB Command Signal Flow\n(brake pressure + AEB domain state -> EHB control and pressure command)

participant "Brake / AEB inputs" as BrakeCtx #F4F7FB
participant "EHB\nbrake-hydraulic owner" as EHB #E8F7E8
participant "EHB state bus" as EhbBus #FFF4CC
participant "Observers / brake users" as Obs #E8F0FE

== Brake Inputs ==

BrakeCtx -> EHB : brakePressure\naebStopReq / aebDecelProfile / aebDomainHealth
EHB -> EHB : if brake stale then\nbrakePressure = 0
EHB -> EHB : if AEB stale then\nstopReq = 0 / decelProfile = 0 / domainHealth = 0
EHB -> EHB : aebPressureCmd = deriveAebPressureCmd(stopReq, decelProfile, domainHealth)
EHB -> EHB : pressureCmd = max(brakePressure, aebPressureCmd)
EHB -> EHB : ctrlState = 2 when AEB overlay active, else 1 when manual brake > 0
note right of EHB
Representative gating inputs
- brakePressure
- aebStopReq
- aebDecelProfile
- aebDomainHealth
end note

== EHB Publish ==

EHB -> EhbBus : frmEhbStateMsg\nEhbCtrlState / EhbPressureCmd
note right of EHB
Representative outputs
- EhbCtrlState
- EhbPressureCmd
end note

== Downstream Visibility ==

EhbBus -> Obs : hydraulic-brake readback /\nassist overlay consumers

note over BrakeCtx, Obs
Representative runtime chain
1. Manual brake pressure and AEB domain state reach EHB
2. EHB computes the stronger of manual and AEB pressure demands
3. EHB publishes control state and effective pressure command
4. Brake observers consume the final hydraulic command posture
end note

@enduml
